title: Bug 109350: Output parameter does not display in data set dialog.
description: When in the query result page, the output parameter does not appear in the edit data set dialog. This behavior is unexpected and needs to be addressed.
OB: While in the query result page, there is no data returned. The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be visible in the edit data set dialog when in the query result page.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Navigate to the query result page.
2. Note the absence of any returned data.
3. Open the edit data set dialog.
4. Observe that the output parameter is not displayed.
